The Story of Uhrlik<br>
The whole of earthly emotion<br>
<br>
Uhrlik had spent much time on the lost continent of Kunark. He had slain the vicious Sarnak in the Lake of Ill Omen; he had teamed up with Amarante again to slay giants in the Frontier Mountains. He even went to the Overthere to combat the powerful creatures there, but he left soon after finding that the Dragoons in the outpost there had a particular hatred for him.<br>
